asset.author: charbroil
asset.hookText:
The Char-Broil Rip-Stop cover is 7X stronger than regular grill covers. We decided to put this claim to the test! We shot potatoes at over 300 mph at a regular grill cover and the new Char-Broil Rip-Stop cover to see if it would tear and penetrate the covers. We found out that even when loaded with rocks, our potato cannon couldn't rip the Rip-Stop cover. Take a look and see for yourself! 

If you want to see more potato carnage (including what happens to a grill when you launch potatoes at it, visit http://live.charbroil.com/ripstop.
